      <title>道明银行在美国洗钱调查中获得 4.5 亿美元赔偿</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/td-takes-450-million-provision-in-us-money-laundering-probe</link>
      <description><![CDATA[多伦多道明银行 (Toronto-Dominion Bank) 已就美国对其反洗钱行为持续进行的监管和执法调查而提取了 4.5 亿美元的初步准备金，并表示预计将面临更多处罚。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/td-takes-450-million-provision-in-us-money-laundering-probe</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 21:40:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>看到企业客户之间在现金利率上的分歧：富国银行的麦克迈克尔</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-30/seeing-divide-between-corporate-clients-on-cash-rates-wells-fargo-s-mcmichael</link>
      <description><![CDATA[富国银行企业和公共实体战略主管凡妮莎·麦克迈克尔(Vanessa McMichael)表示，一些客户正在利用美联储可能长期暂停的机会来维持现金利率，而其他客户则看到了机会。她与彭博社的 Romaine Bostick 和 Alix Steel 就“彭博市场：收盘”进行了交谈。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-30/seeing-divide-between-corporate-clients-on-cash-rates-wells-fargo-s-mcmichael</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 21:22:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Jeremy Hunt 警告英国 FCA 的“点名与羞辱”计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/jeremy-hunt-warns-against-uk-fca-s-name-and-shame-plans</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国财政大臣杰里米·亨特就英国金融监管机构在早期阶段公布其正在调查的公司的计划向英国金融监管机构发出警告，这是针对英国最高金融监管机构的罕见政治干预。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/jeremy-hunt-warns-against-uk-fca-s-name-and-shame-plans</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 21:20:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>彭博市场与 Sonali Basak 04/30/2024</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-30/bloomberg-markets-with-sonali-basak-04-30-2024</link>
      <description><![CDATA[《彭博市场》追踪全球所有资产类别的市场走势，并讨论华尔街面临的最大问题。在今天的节目中，Sonali Basak 与 CFRA 股票研究副总裁 Arun Sundaram 进行了交谈。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-30/bloomberg-markets-with-sonali-basak-04-30-2024</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 21:06:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>PG&E 正与 KKR 洽谈出售电力业务少数股权</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/pg-e-in-talks-with-kkr-to-sell-minority-stake-in-power-business</link>
      <description><![CDATA[PG&amp;E Corp. 表示，正在就将其发电业务的少数股权出售给投资公司 KKR &amp; E 进行谈判。公司参与了一项监管机构已表示不打算支持的交易。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/pg-e-in-talks-with-kkr-to-sell-minority-stake-in-power-business</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 21:04:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>不断增长的人工智能需求刺激了亚马逊的盈利</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-30/rising-ai-demand-spurs-amazon-earnings-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚马逊周二在一份声明中表示，该公司第一季度收入增长 13%，达到 1,433 亿美元，而分析师平均预期为 1,426 亿美元。埃德·勒德洛 (Ed Ludlow) 在彭博电视台 (Bloomberg Television) 上有更多报道。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-30/rising-ai-demand-spurs-amazon-earnings-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 20:37:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
